snippet.title: Slime Rancher - In Stores Now!
snippet.description:
Explore the Far, Far Range with the new boxed edition of Slime Rancher on PS4 and Xbox One!

Every box includes: Digital Download for the Original Soundtrack, 10% off coupon for Fangamer Merchandise, and a Slimepedia Booklet.

Buy now online or at your local game shop!
